engineCMS::localVars()

Description
    public bool engineCMS::localVars(string $variable [, mixed $value = NULL [, bool $null = FALSE]])
    Adds a variable/value pair to the localVars array.

Parameters
    variable
        A name for the variable.
    value
	The variable's value.  Default value is NULL.
    null
	
Return Values
    Returns TRUE on success or FALSE on failure.

Examples

	Example #1
	    <?php
		...
		$engine->localVars('pageTitle', "WVU Libraries: eNotification");
		...
	    ?>

	Example #2
	    <?php
		...
		$engine->localVars('siteRoot', $engineVars['WEBROOT']. "/enotification");
		...
	    ?>
Notes
   
